= Minor Factions

As the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> is a diverse party, there are also many minor groups all pushing for their voices to be heard.

[? if mr_gyatt:Thanks to our efforts to gain support in Rural Germany, Fritz Baade has arrived to the congress, as the new head of an <span style="color: #38C538;">**Agrarian Wing**</span> of our party. Not much is known about what he aims to propose, we will have to wait until the congress starts. ?]

As radicalism is on the rise in Germany, there exists a small <span style="color: #800020;">Neorevisionist wing</span>. Only time will tell where this will go from here.

[? if mr_skibidi:In addition, our increased support among the <span style="color: #a0a0a0;">**Middle Class**</span> has resulted in the creation of an interest group to push for moderation and progressive reforms within the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span>. ?]

